imdb.plot outline: A heightened and satirical comedy following actresses Arielle Vandenberg and Cara Santana, The Unt. Arielle Vandenberg and Cara Santana project is an insiders look at what it takes to "make it" in Hollywood. Complete with celebrity cameos and real life inspiration, the scripted series follows real life friends Arielle and Cara, who couldn't be more different but have the same goal, as they navigate (somewhat untraditionally, somewhat factually) their dreams in of being serious actresses.
